<p>Now I am using the <code>tab-bar</code> workflow I noticed that <code>winner-mode</code> was not working per tab in that the winner undo would return to the previous state of another tab, pretty annoying! ðŸ˜•</p>
<figure><img src="https://emacs.dyerdwelling.family/ox-hugo/20240114145517-emacs--Winner-Undo-To-Tab-Bar-History.jpg" width="100%">
</figure>

<p>But there is an easy fix, replace <code>(winner-mode 1)</code> with <code>(tab-bar-history-mode 1)</code></p>
<p>and for example I replaced my following keybindings:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-elisp" data-lang="elisp"><span style="display:flex;"><span>(global-set-key (kbd <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;M-u&#34;</span>) <span style="color:#e6db74">&#39;winner-undo</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>(global-set-key (kbd <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;M-i&#34;</span>) <span style="color:#e6db74">&#39;winner-redo</span>)
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>with</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-elisp" data-lang="elisp"><span style="display:flex;"><span>(global-set-key (kbd <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;M-u&#34;</span>) <span style="color:#e6db74">&#39;tab-bar-history-back</span>)
</span></span><span style="display:flex;"><span>(global-set-key (kbd <span style="color:#e6db74">&#34;M-i&#34;</span>) <span style="color:#e6db74">&#39;tab-bar-history-forward</span>)
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>Ironically I had just been reading a related section in <strong>Mastering Emacs</strong> and this configuration was recommended to avoid confusion and general vexation.</p>
<p>I would also recommend increasing the number of tab bar history elements remembered, the default is 10 and I quickly found myself running out.</p>
<p>Therefore I put in:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;"><code class="language-elisp" data-lang="elisp"><span style="display:flex;"><span>(setq tab-bar-history-limit <span style="color:#ae81ff">100</span>)
</span></span></code></pre></div>